<div class="text-sm-center m-5">
<h1 id="intro" class="display-3 m-2 text-sm-center mb-5">BACKLOGGER</h1>
	<h2 class="display-4">Login Page</h2>
	<%= form_tag(sessions_path, method: "post") do 	%>
		<%= label_tag(:username, "Username", class: "	m-1") %><br>
	 	<%= text_field_tag(:username) %><br>
	
	 	<%= label_tag(:password, "Password", class: "	m-1") %><br>
	 	<%= password_field_tag(:password) %><br>
	
	 	<%= submit_tag("Login", class: "m-2 	btn-primary") %>
	<% end %>
	<h3 class= "mb-4 mr-2 mt-5">Welcome To Backlogger!</h3>
	<p class="lead">How many times have you seen a preview for a movie, been loaned a world-famous novel, or shell out a pretty penny for that hot new ps4 title, only to have life's day to day chaos bury the experience, never to be seen again?</p>
	<h4>WELL I SAY NO MORE!</h4>
	<p>Backlogger will give you a platform to store these experiences so you will never have to miss out again!</p>
	<div class="container">
		<ul class="no-bullet">
			<li>Want to see what movies, games or books you've missed?<span class="bold"> WE'VE GOT YOU COVERED!</span></li>
			<li>Is there an item that should be here that isn't?<span class='bold'> CREATE IT!</span></li>
			<li>Wouldn't it be awesome if on top of saving, you can store a list of all of your completed items?<span class="bold"> YOU GOT IT!</span></li>
		</ul>
		<p class="lead">Sooooo what are you still reading this for?<span class="bold"> GET BACKLOGGING!</span></p>
	</div>
</div>